<HEAD>Cartoonist Aims This Week's Barbs At Albert Gore</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NASHVILLE, Tenn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Tennessee Sen. Albert Gore Junior's
quest for the Democratic presidential nomination comes under the
scrutiny of ``Doonesbury'' cartoonist Garry Trudeau this week.
   Beginning with Monday's strip, Trudeau takes a week-long look at
Gore's childhood, his Tennessee political career and his bid for
